DJANGO PROJECT WITH:

-HTML5 boilerplate: http://html5boilerplate.com/
-Webassets
 -960.gs
 -Sass
-Freshen
-Django-nose 
-Dotcloud deployment

DOTCLOUD:

For more information to deploy Django on dotcloud visit:
http://docs.dotcloud.com/tutorials/django/

Deployment:

Step 1 install the dotcloud cli:
pip install -r requirements_local.txt

Step 2 create the namespace:
dotcloud create namespace

Stop 3 create the service:
dotcloud create -t python namespace.service

Step 4 (this requires git or hg):
dotcloud push namespace.service .
